text: @senatemajldr The “models” predicting COVID19 deaths are Worldwide ... right now we sit at 38k WW. ... some of these deaths would have happened without COVID-19 .... the peak is expected in 3 weeks ... so if the 38k doubles each week then the Worldwide deaths will be 300k the end of April ...
